{
  "stem": "25423.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They administered law, because Jews refrain from going to courts.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were spiritual leaders of the community, and very highly-regarded and respected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Rarely, if ever, they were paid a very generous salary.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they-- their lifestyle was relatively modest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "My impression is, is my father was a chief rabbi of a very large, very wealthy community.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was paid-- looking at it from my perspective today-- adequately.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were not in a need.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But my impression is that we could not afford too many luxuries.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "However, my mother was a rather wealthy, because her father was an estate owner-- very large estate.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Primarily a residential.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I went first to public school in Lwow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the public school system, which was left over by Austro-Hungary, was excellent.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the school's name was Adam Mickiewicz, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a very famous Polish writer and poet-- more or less a contemporary of Byron and Pushkin.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Was a very fine school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There I finished six grades.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The composition of the city has, in a way, determined the composition of children in the school.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One third was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One third was Polish, and one third was Lithuanian or Ukrainian.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--in the classes as well?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, no.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How about the staff, the teachers?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Were they all Polish or-- All Polish.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Polish primarily.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Jews were teaching in some schools, but it was not common to see many Jewish teachers in the public school system.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was a curiosity because, first of all, my father was a leader of men and leader of the community and well-known in Jewish and non-Jewish circles.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Secondly, because of the position of my father, I did not attend school on Saturdays which, in a way, was a handicap.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
